By playing on our servers you automatically accept all of the rules listed below.
Ignorance of server rules does not relieve you of responsibility!
Not for all violations of the rules they ban players, what the administration of the project decides to do with violators!
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Raid

1.1. Mass raiding is prohibited (genocide) - ban by steam;
*A raid is any manifestation of aggression against a base or animals on it (killing more than 5 pcs.) - grief.

1.2. You cannot raid more than one tribe per day (cooldown drops at 00:00 Moscow time). This also applies to the PvE mode - killing animals on the basis of the enemy is considered a raid. If someone attacks your base, then the limit on raid 1 tribe per day is automatically removed, but only in relation to the attackers (have proof with you). You can also raid the second tribe by mutual consent to the war (attach screenshots of the chat as evidence of consent);

1.2.1. You cannot constantly raid the same tribe and prevent them from developing within 2 days after the raid. If, for some reason, you didn’t raid a tribe, you can return once within two hours. If you have not returned within two hours, then you turn on the cd for the re-raid of this tribe;
*Buildings left after the raid will be demolished! (if you do not take them with you)

1.4. All tribal conflicts and disputes (insider) - players decide among themselves (do not write and complain to the administration). If a member of the tribe for some reason killed you, robbed, broke the house, branded or killed the animals of the tribe, then you are to blame for this, the administration is not involved in your personal problems;

1.5. The deaf building of animals and Tek Hover Skiff is forbidden, on a maximum of two sides, in the head and tail of the building should not protrude beyond the platform at the distance of the 1st foundation (cannot be discharged by buildings) - killing the animal without warning;

1.6. It is forbidden to put huge buildings on platform saddles (frames, hatches, large walls, etc.);

1.6.1. It is forbidden to build pipes / tunnels on platforms and being in them sculpt C4 on other people's buildings;
*A pipe on a platform is considered to be a box on a platform larger than 2x1 of the foundation. Walls in height are also considered a pipe!

1.7. It is forbidden to use animals to cause damage through textures:
1. Get up a Giga in the passage into the cave and gnaw through the rocks (when the head is in the textures)
2. Shoot the Velonasaur through stones / textures
3. Use Tapejara with a tech saddle, shooting through buildings / textures);

1.7.1. It is forbidden to use animals to defuse turrets due to the penetration of their limbs through textures;

1.8. It is forbidden to use buildings on platforms, including buildings on a raft or a motor boat, to enter other buildings to undermine;
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. Communication

2.1. It is forbidden to insult other players, members of the community and administration. (3 comments and departure from the server, any previous warnings are considered);

2.2. It is forbidden to flood / spam in the game chat and in the group comments in VK;

2.3. Advertising of other servers is prohibited; selling accounts, prints, things and resources in the game chat, to a group in VK and to discord;

2.4. It is forbidden to use nicknames that contain: mat, obscene expressions, racism, extremism, idiomatic and criminal expressions, plagiarism, advertising, pornography, eroticism, threats of violence, any other information that is offensive in relation to other players and the administration;

2.5. It is forbidden to use a nickname mentioning the administrator, administration. It is also impossible to introduce themselves as admins, thereby misleading players.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. Cheats / Textures / Bugs

3.1. For the use of any cheats, bugs, dups - ban on Steam;

3.2. For the intentional use of something to put the server - a ban on Steam;

3.3. It is forbidden to climb and build in textures;

3.4. It is forbidden to use the refrigerator for firing from it;

3.5. It is forbidden to put turrets on invisible buildings;

3.6. It is forbidden to build in the air without connecting to the surface and without supporting the foundation under or above them (under water, too);

3.6.1. It is forbidden to go around the distance to the construction of buildings near another tribe (due to height or depth);

3.7. For using S + Tek Teleport and Awesome Teleport for getting into textures - ban on Steam;

3.7.2. It is forbidden to put more than two MAGA ORP poles on a tribe. When merging the tribes, remove the extra columns;

3.8. For the destruction of elemental veins by animals (for example mantis) on PvE servers, which is branded by another player - a ban on Steam.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. Development

4.1. It is forbidden to place bunkers or any buildings near other bases in order to limit the possibility of their development (being in PvE mode). And also about the bases of players who are in PvE mode (even if you already have PvP);

4.2. You cannot have different tribe names in the same cluster;
*You can rename the tribes once a week.

4.2.1. It is forbidden to change the name of the tribe before the raid and after the raid (do not hide yourself);

4.3. It is forbidden to keep the player or his animal (not to let him play) for more than 2 real hours;

4.4. It is forbidden to kill an already sleeping animal or being in a trap;

4.5. It is forbidden to withdraw wild titans from their spawn zone and raid foreign bases by them. The same cannot be done with corrupted animals (this also applies to the x50 pve server);
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5. Construction

5.1. One tribe on the map is allowed to have only one base on land, the second in water (if there was a merger of the tribes, then you will have to sacrifice one of the bases to comply with the rules);

5.2. Building caves without artifacts. The one who first built / blocked the entrance is its owner. Other buildings will be removed!

5.3. It is forbidden to build bases at the players' spawn points, near obelisks and in any holes / crevices with narrow passages in them that are not caves (these also include fences, pillboxes with turrets, spikes, traps, etc.);
*Caves are places where buildings receive increased damage (x6).

5.4. It is forbidden to build or block the passage to any rays or drops while you have active PvE status (you can see with / pvestatus command);

5.5. Ownerless constructions, foundations, columns and stakes are prohibited. They additionally load the server. Please destroy if not in use;
*Allowed only near their base.

5.5.1. It is forbidden to scatter bunkers / fob on the server, you can only put it near your own or another's base during a raid / defense. An exception is the protection of oneself at the obelisk during the passage of the boss and the defense of a drop or core on an Extintion;

5.6. It is forbidden to open Awesome Teleport publicly to everyone. If you accidentally teleported to someone else's base, then take screenshots with the name of the teleport and to whom it belongs;
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

6. Administration

6.1. The project administration is not responsible for game bugs: the disappearance of animals or loot, falling through textures, stuck in textures, stuck animals in a cryopod, etc. All this is on the conscience of the developers of the game;
* Exceptions in the event of a server crash (log screens should be attached).

6.2. The administration does not bear any responsibility for the contents of the cryocapsules, as well as for themselves;

6.3. For ignoring administration warnings - ban;

6.4. The administration at its discretion may block access to the server of any player or group of players, without explanation and reasons (this is a necessary measure);

6.5. The administration has the right to amend existing rules to improve the quality of the game for our players;

6.6. We have individual server settings, if they do not suit you, we do not hold you.

